net.proteusframework.ui.management.nav

Class NavigableBuilder<N extends Navigable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.management.nav.NavigableBuilder<N>
  • Type Parameters:
    N - navigable type.

    @Configurable
public class NavigableBuilder<N extends Navigable>
extends Object
    Configuration builder for navigable mechanisms. This is a convenience class for setting NavigationLink.setNavigationDestinationResolver(NavigationDestinationResolver) and NavigationLink.setPropertyValueResolver(PropertyValueResolver)

    At a minimum, one of the to methods must be called.

    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
